description: You feel uneasy here as if some evil magic is being cast on you.
You suspect something fishy is going on in here.
9353.name: Inside a Gigantic Clam

description: You are on the very edge of the galaxy.  Nothing is here except that there
is a path which leads down.
9318.name: Edge of the Galaxy

description: You have reached the end of the mystic chains.  Looking up, you notice a
small landing on which you can climb.  However, there seems to be another
forcefield blocking your way.
9354.name: End of the Mystic Chains

description: You see the forcefield of Summer.
You see the forcefield of Spring.
You are approaching the leg part of this creature.  You look around and see
that the surrounding is all dark except for some faint lights from the
distant stars.
9358.name: Near the Legs of Draco

description: You are still wandering around this temple.  You notice exits lie in all
directions except west.
9327.name: Western Side of the Temple

description: This is the Throne room of the King of the Universe.  From here you can see
every star and constellation in the Universe.
9367.name: Cepheus' Throne

description: It is the chamber of the prince, Perseus.  However, he seems not to be here.
Maybe he has gone to get Pegasus to save Andromeda?
9334.name: Perseus' Chamber

description: From above you can faintly make out the gigantic arms which extend far
beyond into the darkness.
9361.name: Near the Arms of Draco

description: You are on the highest peak of the Universe.  You look around and notice
clouds below you.  One of the clouds resembles a goat-like form.
9351.name: On a Mountain Peak

description: You are still wandering around this temple.  You notice exits lie in all
directions except east.
9333.name: Eastern Side of the Temple

description: Indeed it is too bright to tell.  Because what you are witnessing is the
rare event of a Supernova, how a star explodes itself into galactic dust.
You may find yourself lucky to witness this rare event but even luckier,
you have finally got out of this galaxy as your body turns into dust.
That really HURTS!
9320.name: Too Bright to Tell

description: Nearby you can hear the roar of an animal.  Peering through the dense
overgrowth you think you glimpse a pair of menacing eyes.
9346.name: Within the Deep Jungle

description: You are still wandering around this temple.  You notice exits lie in all
directions except north.
9329.name: Northern Side of the Temple

description: You are inside a small clearing.  You can see that there are signs of a
living creature nearby.
9317.name: Small Clearing

description: You wonder why the galaxy is limited.  All you have done in Astronomy
courses now prove worthless.  Well who told you to take one at the start?
9323.name: Corner of the Galaxy

description: This bridge has been made by the stars to honour their ancestors.  The
bridge itself shines brightly and makes you feel that you are walking on
a path of light.
9308.name: On the Bridge of Stars

description: You are still travelling inside this path of mist.  You notice a small
opening to the east.
9313.name: Along the Milky Way

description: You are standing inside the dock of a court.  You feel an overwhelming
sense of guilt and you want to protest your innocence!  You fear retribution
and feel yourself exposed, just like the trees in Autumn.
9348.name: Supreme Court

description: You are very near to a gigantic red star.  While you are still fascinated
by its beauty, the star keeps on growing ... suddenly you realize that you'd
better leave.
9319.name: Very Near to a Gigantic Star

description: This place looks deserted, covered with space debris.  Not a sign of life
is around.
9306.name: Undeveloped Part of the Galaxy

description: You have entered into this old temple, which was built originally for the gods
in Mount Olympia, but it is now deserted as someone took over this part of the
Universe.
9331.name: Entrance of the Ancient Temple

description: At last you are half way through this long, weary journey. You can see
the wings are to the east but it seems that another forcefield is in the way.
9359.name: On the Back of Draco

description: You see the forcefield of Autumn.
Suddenly you find yourself on a hillside.  As you look around, you notice
that Spring has descended upon you.
9342.name: On a Hill

description: Just as you started enjoying this journey inside the mist, you have come to
the end of it.  West leads to a bridge and east leads to somewhere else.
9314.name: At the End of the Milky Way

description: This is another uninhabited place.  Exits lie north, east and south.
9322.name: Another Edge of the Galaxy

description: A peaceful feeling overtakes you.  You see a magnificent four-poster bed.
It's a double bed and there is only room for one more!  Well, what now ... ?
9347.name: Inside a Luxurious Bedroom

description: You see stars around you but nothing of special interest.
9366.name: Along the Path of the Dipper

description: The noise is deafening.  You are about to take a drink when you realize
that the water is being poured out of a vessel of mind-boggling proportions!
9352.name: Inside a Waterfall

description: You notice the walkway has come to an abrupt end and you wonder why. You see
that there is still a small path which leads north and one to the west.
To the east lies a bridge.
9305.name: End of the InterGalactic Walkway

description: You are dangling on the chains.  You notice exits lie in all directions.
Up above you see the chains continue upwards.  But a forcefield prevents
you from going further upwards.
9339.name: On the Mystic Chains

description: You see the forcefield of Spring.
This bridge, like the other, was made as a memorial.  The nebulae had to
make one just to show that they are as capable as the stars.  North lies
a throne room.
9309.name: On the Bridge of Nebulae

description: You realize you are standing on scaly ground.  As you wonder what the ground
is made of, you feel the ground move.
9355.name: On the Draco

description: You have come to the end of Draco, but you can't find the head!
You see a forcefield to the south, some distance away, beyond reach.
If only the head were here ...
9363.name: Approaching the Head of Draco

description: You see the forcefield of Winter.
You see stars around you but nothing of special interest.
9368.name: Along the path of the Dipper

description: You are now lost in space.  Compasses don't work here, sorry.  What's more
you can sense darkness engulfing you.  You'd better get out quick.
9324.name: Lost in Space

description: You are inside the home of the stars.  All you can see around you are stars
and nothing else.  You eyes become pretty hurt as you look at them.
9321.name: Star Cluster

description: Your journey is now approaching the end.  However, this neck seems to be
endless.
9362.name: On the Neck of Draco

description: You are on a well-paved path which seems that it was made deliberately for
visitors like you.  The walkway continues north and a small exit lies west.
9304.name: On an InterGalactic Walkway

description: Now you are in the innermost part of the galaxy.  What you are walking on now
is the path of the Great Dipper or the Plough.  You notice that there are
seven rooms in this zone, representing the seven stars of the Dipper.
9364.name: Entrance of the Great Dipper

description: You see the forcefield of Winter.

9307.name: Tunnel of Stars

description: You find yourself in the center of a Centaurion hunting party.  You'd better
hide yourself before you become the 'center attraction'!
9350.name: In the Woods

description: You stand on a strange ethereal plain, beneath you swirling the
dreamscape of Divided Souls.  West lies the Galaxy, while the strange
passageway leads down.
9302.name: At the Fringe of Dreams

description: You stand before the throne of a long-forgotten hero.  It is full of bounty
that he got from the Ten Labours.
9332.name: Hercules' Mighty Throne

description: This is the sacred offering chamber in which sacrifices are made.  You see a
young girl here, chained to the wall, as if she is waiting for execution.
You look up and realize the chains are sent down directly from above.
Below you recognize the temple of Thalos.
9330.name: Offering Chamber

description: You are inside what used to be a ground for bull fighting.  But you notice
there are no Matadors around.  Maybe they are all dead?
9343.name: Inside a Spanish Bull-Ring

description: You are confused by the shifting sands around you.  Through the shimmering
heat you see the hazy outline of a giant scorpion ... is this a mirage?
9349.name: In the Dry Desert

description: You hear some giant flapping sounds nearby.  You desperately try to get hold
of something as the forceful gusts sweep you away.
9360.name: Between the Wings of Draco

description: This is dedicated to the Great Hunter of all time -- Orion.
Scattered on the floor is the famous hunting equipment used by him.
9328.name: Orion's Hunting Lodge

description: This is a strange study. Besides the desks and chairs you also see a large
mirror in the middle.  So, you wonder, is this how you make a Gemini into
two Gemini?
9344.name: Inside a study

description: This is where the famous Seven Sisters live.  You'd better not disturb them.
9326.name: Homes of the Pleiades

description: You have finished the path of the Dipper.  Here, the most prominent feature
is a set of claw-marks.  You also notice a room to the south; it looks as
if Polaris could lie here.
9370.name: End of the Dipper

description: You are now inside the galaxy, around you you see stars and nebulae smiling
at your presence, and comets and meteors wandering around you.  You realize
that this world may not be the true galaxy after all, but just another
fantasy zone.  Exits lie virtually in all directions.
9303.name: Inside the Galaxy

description: At last you realize that you are on a giant snake-like dragon called the
Draco, the guardian of the inner galaxy.  You realize that the Draco is
actually flying now!
9356.name: Tail of the Draco

description: You start to feel the heat of Summer.  Amongst the rocky beach you notice
hidden forms which could be camouflaged crabs.
9345.name: Along the seashore

description: You are inside a dimly-lit room.  The atmosphere makes you feel uncomfortable.
In front of you stands a mysterious gypsy.  She whispers 'Your fate and
destiny lie beyond this world.'  You are still wondering what she means when
you suddenly notice the crystal ball ... it glows fiercely and displays the
Universe!
9301.name: Inside a Tavern

description: The shadows cloud your vision.
You can only faintly make out that it is a throne room as it is too
dark in here.  In the middle is an empty throne.  You wonder where
the King has gone, maybe he is hiding from you?
9310.name: Throne Room of the Nebula King

description: It is here that the famous old Milky Way starts flowing.  You are surrounded
by streams of mist the moment you tread on it.  You can't see well in
here ... luckily you haven't fallen yet!
9312.name: At the Start of the Milky Way

description: Well you have chosen the wrong path, sorry.  Nothing can escape from this
monster, not even light.
PANIC!  You can't escape!
9325.name: Black Hole

description: This is the Throne room of the Queen of the Universe.  From here you can see
every star and constellation in the Universe.
9365.name: Cassiopeia's Throne

description: You see stars around you but nothing of special interest.
9369.name: Along the path of the Dipper

description: As you struggle along this scaly creature you realize that the only way
you can reach to the inner galaxy is by going all the way to the head.
9357.name: Path of the Draco

description: You will become him if you are not careful.
9301.room_name: A poor mudder, lost in this place.
9301.name: a poor mudder~

description: You can't tell what the star looks like, she is too bright!
9302.room_name: A beautiful white star smiles at you.
9302.name: a beautiful star~

description: It hasn't got a definite shape, it is just a cloud of mist.
9303.room_name: A young nebula, waiting to become a star.
9303.name: a young nebula~

description: You see the offspring of Halley's comet, here just to wipe everything out.
9304.room_name: A speedy comet is waiting to crush your head in.
9304.name: a speedy comet~

description:
You notice the giant is not as tough as his name sounds ...
Still he can be very powerful.
9305.room_name: An enormous, red supergiant is forced to protect the galaxy.
9305.name: a red supergiant~

description:
Like the red giant, he is also appointed to stand guard for the galaxy.
But somehow he manages to escape.  Though tiny, it can take a lot of hits!
9306.room_name: A tiny white dwarf is trying to sneak away from duty.
9306.name: a white dwarf~

description:
You can only make out its shape from the darkness.  He was cursed to stay in
here and his face may never be seen by anyone again.
9307.room_name: A huge nebula is here, resembling a horsehead.
9307.name: a horsehead nebula~

description:
She was once a princess of beauty.  However, her beauty has led to a Goddess's
jealousy and she has to suffer here endlessly until Perseus comes.
9308.room_name: The poor Andromeda is chained to the wall, suffering ...
9308.name: poor Andromeda~

description:
He has been put to do the Ten Labours -- ten impossible tasks, by Hera, the
queen goddess, who disliked him.  But he finished them all and at the end was
granted immortality. He is a very brave and strong fighter.
9309.room_name: The Mighty Hercules is working hard on his extra Labours for the Gods.
9309.name: the mighty Hercules~

description: It is the legendary horse with wings on its back.
9310.room_name: The wild pegasus is grazing peacefully.
9310.name: the wild Pegasus~

description:
He is the legendary hunter who almost defeated Taurus the bull, but got
killed by Scorpio.  The gods put them both up as constellations but one
appears on one side of the sky and the other the other side so they will
never meet.
9311.room_name: Orion is still hunting for Scorpio.
9311.name: Orion the hunter~

description:
These are the seven sisters of the Myths, and as for why they are here, no
one knows; even the Gods themselves have forgotten.
9312.room_name: The Pleiades are here, weeping for the loss of their sisters.
9312.name: the Pleiades~

description:
This evil-looking head is even larger than a giant.  He is the last guardian 
before entering the inner galaxy.  His neck is flexing in a random fashion so 
hitting the head is certainly not easy.
9313.room_name: The gigantic Head of Draco lurks out from beneath and prepares to roast you.
9313.name: the Head of Draco~

description:
You see a tiny creature which looks like a dragon except that its body
resembles a snake.  Gosh, is this a draco, you wonder, is this the thing
we are on now?
9314.room_name: A baby draco is crawling on the Draco's body.
9314.name: a baby draco~

description:
You see a white goat here, the first guardian of the Zodiac,
also the ruler of Spring. He looks as if he is expecting you.
9315.room_name: Aries is sitting here, welcoming you.
9315.name: Aries~

description:
You see a wild-looking bull with a bad temper.  He is well-built and looks like 
he can fight well ... indeed he has fought with Orion before and survived.
9316.room_name: Taurus wants to leave, but has been forced to stay as a guardian here.
9316.name: Taurus~

description:
As soon as you see him you know that he is the most perfect man you have seen.
You can't find any imperfections on him.
9317.room_name: Gemini is looking for his brother; have you seen him?
9317.name: Gemini~

description:
As soon as you see him you see the most imperfect man you have ever seen.
How can there be such a contrast?  You wonder ...
9318.room_name: Gemini is hiding from his brother, grinning evilly at you.
9318.name: Gemini~

description:
You see a gigantic crab (YES, it is bigger than you!) with a crushed shell.
Legend is that he was crushed by Hercules when he was sent by Hera to kill him.
So Hera made Cancer a constellation for his work.
9319.room_name: Cancer the crab is here, hoarding the treasure away from you.
9319.name: Cancer~

description:
His metallic skin means that he could be the one which was killed by Hercules
during his first Labour.  His skin is so weapon-proof that Hercules had to use
his bare hands to tear the lion into two from its mouth!
9320.room_name: Leo the lion is roaring at you, ready for a strike!
9320.name: Leo~

description:
From what you have seen, you now realize that legends are legends, and Virgo
may not be the maid of chastity and purity at all!  But still she looks
gorgeous and is waiting for your first move, whatever it is ...
9321.room_name: Virgo is sitting here, winking at you suggestively ... you are alarmed!
9321.name: Virgo~

description:
He is a wise old man and can see people's thoughts through their eyes....
Now all he can see from you is greed and bloodshed.
9322.room_name: Libra, the fair and just, is staring at you, weighing up the sins of your past.
9322.name: Libra~

description:
Ever since he killed Orion in the myths, he has been punished by having 
Sagittarius' arrow aimed at his heart forever.
9323.room_name: Scorpio is moving his tail towards you, waiting to put an end to some mortals.
9323.name: Scorpio~

description: He is a centaur and a well trained archer. No one can escape his arrows.
9324.room_name: Sagittarius the centaur is waiting to let go of his well aimed arrow ...
9324.name: Sagittarius~

description:
You see a mean-looking ram here.  He used to be a fierce fighter in the ancient
war but now the gods have decided to put him here, to live out the rest of his 
days in peace.
9325.room_name: Capricorn is here, feeling bored ... he wants a fight!
9325.name: Capricorn~

description:
The pretty Water Bearer is smiling at you, you think you'd better give her a 
hand with holding the vessel.
9326.room_name: The beautiful Aquarius is standing here, holding THE vessel.
9326.name: Aquarius~

description:
She has been forced to serve her husband, who had been cursed to turn into a
fish and she deserves your pity.
9327.room_name: Pisces the mermaid is sitting here, waiting for your help.
9327.name: Pisces the mermaid~

description:
He was once a very handsome man but now has turned into an ugly big fish.
So he becomes jealous of any living thing which is more handsome than him.
9328.room_name: Pisces the fish, is jealous of your approach...
9328.name: Pisces the fish~

description:
The Huge Bear which resides in the northern skies is here. 
You think you'd better turn back.  At least you have got a chance of survival.
9329.room_name: Ursa Major the bear is the last defense against any intruders.
9329.name: Ursa Major the bear~

description: She is the Queen of Dignity; facing her you feel all your dignity has gone.
9330.room_name: Cassiopeia, the queen of the Universe, is sitting on her throne.
9330.name: Cassiopeia the Queen~

description:
He is the King of Might as well as of the Universe. You suddenly feel very
weak and useless in front of him.
9331.room_name: Cepheus, the king of the Universe, is sitting on his throne.
9331.name: Cepheus the King~

description:
He is the Master of the Universe, (NOT He-Man!), the most powerful!  
Even the King and the Queen obey him.  As you look at him you notice he is 
actually a STAR, with dazzling bright light ... maybe you shouldn't have come
here at all?
9332.room_name: Polaris, the polar star, who commands the whole Universe, stands before you!
9332.name: Polaris, the polar star~
